
REQUIREMENTS:

- Gentoo
- app-portage/portage-utils (qatom)
- sys-apps/coreutils (sort)
- sys-apps/findutils (xargs)
- sys-apps/grep (grep)
- sys-apps/portage  (portageq)
- sys-apps/sed (sed)

USAGE:

 git clone <REPO>
 source <Path/To/Clone>/init.sh

 mkdir -p /tmp/sets/
 ETC_PORTAGE_SETS=/tmp/sets/ gen_perl_upgrade_sets 5.22 5.24

 sudo cp /tmp/sets/* /etc/portage/sets/*

 sudo emerge -C -va @perl-cleanup
 sudo emerge -va1 @perl-upgrade
